lyrics:
[Verse]
Gory feast unfolds, the king's appetite awakes
Beneath the moon's dim grace, the table we partake
Bodies torn asunder, blood drips from our maws
Devouring flesh and bone, we feast without a pause

[Chorus]
Serrated knives, tearing through the flesh
Mutilation reigns, under the king's request
Screams blend with the echoes of our morbid cheer
Feasting on the living, our taste buds know no fear
